<item>
            <title>[HBASE-4888] Not close ResultScanner cause the cluster abnormal ( RS memory increase)</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-4888</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;A ResultScanner is created in client side, If the user doesn&apos;t invoke the &quot;ResultScanner.close()&quot; ,it happens that the memory of RegionServer increase rapidly and hold for a long time. Finally,the cluster goes to an abnormal status&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
                <environment>&lt;p&gt;CentOS 5.5 final, hadoop-0.20.2-cdh3u1,hbase-0.20.2-cdh3u1&lt;/p&gt;</environment>
